<apex:page showHeader="false" sidebar="false" standardStylesheets="false">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Salesforce Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .logo {
            /* Standard size restored */
            max-width: 250px; 
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .test-note {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .link-box {
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0070d2;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #0070d2;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .bold-text {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="container">
     
     <img src="{!$Resource.LM_LOGO_bigger}" 
     onerror="this.style.display='none'" 
     alt="Leroy Merlin Logo" 
     class="logo" />
     

        <h1>Portal LMCARE LMQA</h1>

        <p>
            Caso pretendas aceder ao portal comunidades LMQA, poderá fazê-lo por <a href="https://leroymerlin--lmqa.sandbox.my.site.com/autocrat/s/login/" target="_blank">aqui</a>.
        </p>

        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;" />

       
        </div>

       
        <div class="link-box">
    <p>Se tiveres dificuldade no acesso ou necessitares de criação de acesso deves contactar:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0;">
        <li>marco.a.silva@leroymerlin.pt</li>
